      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.On2ZrPJTe8FURsXY]{Operative Exploit}</p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">After you finish moving as part of a @Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.MBNI94tbMoqizPUk]{trick attack} (and before attempting your attack, if you haven&rsquo;t done so already), you can perform a quick, intimidating display that makes any foe adjacent to you @Compendium[sfrpg.conditions.nywSVEeDvp1bk7L3]{shaken} until the beginning of your next turn (Will negates). This shaken condition is suppressed for a creature whenever it is no longer adjacent to you. Once you use this exploit, you can&rsquo;t do so again until you rest for 10 minutes to regain Stamina Points. This is a fear effect.</span> </p>"
